title: Week in politics: Crunch time for new health insurance plans, Trump sued over White House renovations, Americans killed by ISIS
description: Despite being in control of the White House and Congress, Republicans have been unable to pass their health care agenda. We look at why that's the case, as well as a new lawsuit against the president.
